dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init searchPanes.insert` paramater is 'prepend'. Meaning that as standard the panes will appear at the top of the DataTable.


        As standard, SearchPanes will be displayed above the DataTable. However if the value of `-init searchPanes.insert` is set to 'append' then they will be displayed below the DataTable.





$(document).ready(function() {
    $('#example').DataTable( {
        searchPanes:{
            insert: 'append'
        },
		dom: 'Sfrtip'
    });
});
